h2 Two-Factor Authentication
.row.profile_2fa_key
    .column.large-4
        .profile_2fa_qr
            img(src="data:image/png;base64,", alt="")
    .column.large-8
        .profile_2fa_print
            h3 Please write down your authentication key:
            .profile_2fa_print_copy
                input(type="text" value="JJCTGQTDJZAXISTIKJ2VI4TJKA" readonly)
                button.material-icons
                    | content_copy
            button.button.primary.short.spaced
                | PRINT KEY
            .profile_2fa_print_descr
                | Do not save the QR code in any digital form. The QR code must be printedon paper and saved in a secure place, where only you can access it.
.row
    .column.large-7
        form.profile_2fa_form(action="2fa")
            label.profile_settings_info_item
                h4.profile_settings_info_label
                    | Your Authentication Key
                input(type="text" value="JJCTGQTDJZAXISTIKJ2VI4TJKA" readonly)
            label.profile_settings_info_item
                h4.profile_settings_info_label
                    | Insert Your 6-Digit Authentication Code:
                input(type="text")
            button.button.wide.primary.icon
                | Enable two-factor authentication
                i.icon.icon--arrow
    .column.large-5.profile_2fa_info
        .profile_2fa_attention_hex
            span !
        p Always write down your authentication key! You will not be able to log in to your account in case you lose your mobile device.
        p If you are having problems with our system rejecting your authentication code, check your mobile device's clock.
        p It must be synchronized perfectly. Your device will generate a new code every 30 seconds.
        
